OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry through the
OL,6,Fmorning with sunny spells but cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing towards midday. A cloudier
OL,8,Fafternoon with showers spreading
OL,9,Feastwards, but Dundee and the coast
OL,10,Fstaying dry until evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy during the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight with further
OL,14,Fshowers. Becoming mainly dry with
OL,15,Fclear spells towards the end of the
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
