OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry and bright start but a
OL,6,Fband of cloud and patchy rain will
OL,7,Fmove south during the morning. A dry
OL,8,Fafternoon with bright spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Ftouch of frost early Wednesday then
OL,13,Fmainly dry and bright. Rain or showers
OL,14,Fon Thursday and Friday. Feeling rather
OL,15,Fcool for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
